<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Yes/No Webpage</title>
<style>
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;700&display=swap');
body {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;
height: 100vh;
margin: 0;
background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #7ed9c3 40%, #6ba6d8 60%);
font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
}
.container {
text-align: center;
border: 2px solid #d1d1d1;
padding: 20px;
border-radius: 15px;
background-color: #f9f9f9;
box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
max-width: 500px;
}
#yesButton, #noButton {
margin: 10px;
padding: 12px 24px;
font-size: 18px;
border-radius: 25px;
cursor: pointer;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
border: none;
color: #fff;
box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}
#yesButton {
background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #5bd9c3, #3a7ed8); /* Green and blue gradient */
}
#noButton {
background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #3a7ed8, #5bd9c3); /* Blue and green gradient */
}
#prompt {
color: #333;
font-size: 24px;
font-weight: bold;
text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
letter-spacing: 1px;
padding: 20px;
border: 2px solid #d1d1d1;
border-radius: 20px;
background-color: #f5f5f5;
margin-bottom: 20px;
box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
height: 300px;
overflow: auto;
}
#yesButton:hover, #noButton:hover {
transform: scale(1.05);
box-shadow: 0 6px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
}
#yesButton:active, #noButton:active {
transform: scale(0.95);
box-shadow: none;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container" style="background-color: #f9f9f9;">
<div id="prompt" style="color: #333;">
<div style="height: 100%; overflow: auto;">
<p>This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text. This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text. This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text. This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text. This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text. This is a prompt. Do you like this web page? This is a long paragraph that requires scrolling to read the complete text.</p>
</div>
</div>
<button id="yesButton" onclick="alert('You clicked Yes!')">Yes</button>
<button id="noButton" onclick="alert('You clicked No!')">No</button>
</div>
</body>
</html>